stories.title: Samad sets up tight Canada victory
stories.subTitle: Canada v Bermuda, ICC Tri-Series, St Johns
stories.summary: A composed 83 from 86 balls from Abdool Samad - his highest score in 14 ODIs - set Canada up for a tight three-wicket victory over Bermuda in the second match of the Associates Tri-Series at St John's in Antigua
